一隻係珠海入境過黎既豬（未死），無任何防疫證明<br />\n<br />\n係唔係仍然需要由動物管理中心觀察四日，而唔係即時「人道處理」？？動物膠用下個腦先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:57:20.000Z","msg":"因為貓狗高級d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"如果將隻泰國狗換成大陸豬，然後事後有條大陸仔衝出黎話隻大陸豬係寵物豬，話要取回公道，然後有班傻仔又真係呼應大陸仔，為隻豬去「維權」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家就知呢單野有幾單野有幾咁可笑，話緊你呀，鄺俊宇"},{"pid":"988b93c1453936d5fb0e87291be8273a93818a97","tid":1101683,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:13:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b3e9dc78df5b341b3c62080da5b25aa643180b4","tid":1101683,"uid":37869,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d93230225939753939712c3e3e014282a3200e0c","tid":1101683,"uid":51509,"like":3,"dislike":40,"score":-37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"睇完scmp先知原來真係有法例列明流浪狗要觀察四日先可以人道毀滅<br />\n同埋隻狗星期二到香港一日後星期三就已經人道毀滅咗<br />\n咁漁農署呢個做法的確係違法<br />\n唔好因為呢件事激怒左膠就唔記得署方亂做野<br />\n就算係for public good 都唔應該bypass the law<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/society/article/3001617/outrage-over-dog-euthanised-after-reaching-hong-kong-thai\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fsociety%2Farticle%2F3001617%2Foutrage-over-dog-euthanised-after-reaching-hong-kong-thai&h=f741f33a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"6.毀滅動物的權力<br />\n特准人員如有合理理由相信任何動物有以下情形，可將牠毀滅 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)屬違禁動物；<br />\n(b)患有或可能患有狂犬病；或<br />\n(c)曾接觸患有狂犬病的動物。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap421?xpid=ID_1438403181758_002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap421%3Fxpid%3DID_1438403181758_002&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=adc529f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap421?xpid=ID_1438403181758_002</a><br />\n你覺得隻狗來自狂犬病的高風險地區<br />\n算唔算係b, c的情況？"},{"pid":"a2262bb5f001a14d5108c6fdfd0aeab2e6555267","tid":1101683,"uid":177288,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"政府做得冇錯<br />\n的確要盡快人道毀滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來歷不明"}]}